    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team reviewed all thirteen credibility factors and determined that the overall evidence base is sufficient to support the intended use. The Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification provides adequate confidence bounds on hemolysis predictions, and the majority of assessed factors demonstrate credibility levels consistent with the COU requirements. The assessment team concludes that the model is accepted for the stated context of use.",
